com.github.katjahahn.tools.anomalies

Enum AnomalySubType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AnomalySubType>
      • com.github.katjahahn.tools.anomalies.AnomalySubType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AnomalySubType>

    public enum AnomalySubType
extends java.lang.Enum<AnomalySubType>
    Represent the semantics of an anomaly.

    The subtype is a specific description for the anomaly. This avoids having to search for parts of the description string to find certain anomalies.
